==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stealer
<hw>Steal"er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who steals; a thief.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Shipbuilding)</fld> <def>The endmost plank of a
strake which stops short of the stem or stern.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stealing</ent>⟦br⟧
